descriptionHtml:

[B][COLOR=#7f7f7f][SIZE=6][FONT=Garamond]Savegame Details:[/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR][/B]
[LIST][*]Round level 25; sorry don\'t have any earlier saves!
[*]Sharing this mostly for her looks ;)
[/LIST]

[B][COLOR=#7f7f7f][SIZE=6][FONT=Garamond]Prerequisites:[/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR][/B]
[LIST][*]She has been using [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=1175]Elys Uncapper[/url] (Uncaps Level to 300) and [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7015]Uncapped Perks[/url] so you will need them both mostly or it might cause the savegame to crash..!
[*]Textures and meshes i use are [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7127]RANS Headmesh Variants (Type A)[/url], [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666]CBBE[/url], [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7897]Envision Face (Large Lips Edition)[/url], [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6232]Alternative nude Texture[/url], [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12951]Enhanced Character Edit[/url] and the hair is from [url=http://skyrimmod.tistory.com/entry/Skyrim-Tera-Hair-Pack]Tera Hair Pack (External Link)[/url]
[*]Without all that stuff installed she will look different! 
[/LIST]

[B][COLOR=#7f7f7f][SIZE=6][FONT=Garamond]To do:[/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR][/B]
Turn her into a follower ;)
